<div class="centered">
  <% if !flash[:notice].blank? %>
    <div class="alert alert-info">
      <%= flash[:notice] %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <h1 class="main-header">Welcome to the INCS Online Resume Bank</h1>

  <% if session[:user_id] != nil && User.find(session[:user_id]).access == 'pending' %>
    <p>Thank you for your registration. Please allow up to 2 business days for INCS staff to process approval of your account. You have received an email with further information.</p>
  <% end %>

  <% if session[:user_id] == nil %>
    <div class="main-container">
      <%= button_to "Candidate Resume Bank and Job Fair Registration", users_new_teacher_path, method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn"%>
      <%= button_to "School Leader Resume Bank Registration", users_new_school_path, method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn"%>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <h2 class="topic">
    <br>
    2017 INCS Teacher Job Fair
  </h2>

  <p class="main-content">
  The Illinois Network of Charter Schools (INCS) hosted our 12th annual Teacher Job Fair on Saturday, March 18, 2016 at ASPIRA Business & Finance Campus. Representatives from the state’s charter schools will be on hand to recruit hundreds of teachers, social workers, counselors, nurses, and other administrators. INCS seeks highly qualified candidates who are excited to work in a mission-drive environment and to TEACH, LEAD, and SUCCEED. To upload your resume into our <span style="text-decoration: underline">year-round database</span>, please select “Candidate Resume Bank Registration” above.
  </p>



  <p class="main-content">
  <strong>Candidates have the opportunity to:</strong>
  <ul class="main-content-list">
    <li>Meet recruiters from over 50 public charter schools representing over 120 campuses</li>
    <li>Post your resume in the INCS Online Resume Bank, where charter schools look for candidates for various positions year-round</li>
    <li>Interview on-site with schools looking to hire great teachers and administrators like you</li>
  </ul>
  </p>

  <p class="main-content">
  <strong>Schools have the opportunity to:</strong>
  <ul class="main-content-list">
    <li>Meet with hundreds of educators</li>
    <li>View candidates’ resumes and credentials ahead of time using the INCS Online Resume Bank</li>
    <li>Invite candidates for on-site interviews following the meet and greet portion of the event</li>
  </ul>
  </p>

  <p class="main-content"><strong>Agenda</strong></p>
  <p class="main-content">
  <ul class="main-content-list">
    <li>9:00 am - 10:00 pm: School table set-up and Candidate Registration</li>
    <li>10:00 am - 12:00 pm: Meet and greet with Candidates & Schools</li>
    <li>12:00 pm - 1:30 pm: On-site teacher interviews (by invitation only)</li>
  </ul>
  </p>

  <%# <p class="main-content"><strong>Registration</strong></p> %>
  <%# <p class="main-content"> %>
  <%# Candidate check-in will open at 8:30am. <span style="text-decoration: underline">On-site registration is available</span>. Advance registration is encouraged to avoid extended wait times. %>
  <%# </p> %>

  <p class="main-content"><strong>Location</strong></p>
  <p class="main-content">
  ASPIRA Business & Finance Campus, 2989 N. Milwaukee Ave, Chicago, IL 60618
  </p>
  <ul class="main-content-list">
    <li>There will be street parking available. Registered candidates will received updated parking information as it becomes available.</li>
    <li>The school is also accessible by public transportation. It is approximately .5 mile southwest of the Belmont Blue Line stop and is easily accessible via CTA Bus #56 Milwaukee.</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="main-container">
    <%= button_to "School Leader Registration", "https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd2POlBM9yr-WfNbRYFOhnTAZCNg8mfF8gFhfSNKCEm2RACsw/viewform?c=0&w=1", method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn" %>
    <%= button_to "Candidate Registration", users_new_teacher_path, method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn" %>
  </div>

  <p class="main-content"><br>Click <a href="https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.10152791985156379.1073741839.91629716378&type=1">here</a> to view photos of our 2015 INCS Teacher Job Fair, where recruiters from <em>over 120 Illinois charter public school campuses met with</em> highly-qualified applicants for more than <em>500</em> teaching, school leadership, social work, school nurse and administrative positions.
  </p>

  <p class="main-content">
  ATTENTION teacher preparation programs and schools of education: INCS is seeking recruitment partners to support our outreach efforts. Please consider sharing our site with highly qualified candidates.
  </p>

  <!--   <p class="disclaimer">
    *This activity or event is not sponsored by, associated with, or endorsed by the UNO Charter School Network Inc., or its affiliates.
    </p> -->
    <p class="main-content">
    If you have any questions or would like to receive a 2017 Teacher Job Fair flyer, please contact Stephanie Arias, INCS Charter Support Manager, at <%=mail_to("SArias@incschools.org")%>
  </p>

</div>
